SELECT NVL(MAX(HWRECBUEN - HWDESPBUEN - HWRESERVADO),0) AS MAXIMO 
				FROM TIGO.DETINGHW  
					WHERE 1=1 AND (HWRECBUEN - HWDESPBUEN - HWRESERVADO) > 0 AND HWARTCOD = 'ACC0005516'

SELECT HWPACKING,
		HWCAJA,
		HWLINEA,
		HWARTCOD,
		HWRESERVADO,
		HWDESPBUEN,
		HWRECBUEN,
		(HWRECBUEN - HWDESPBUEN - HWRESERVADO) AS DISPONIBLE
		FROM ( 
		SELECT  HWPACKING,
					HWCAJA,
					HWLINEA,
					HWARTCOD,
					HWRESERVADO,
					HWDESPBUEN,
					HWRECBUEN,
					(HWRECBUEN - HWDESPBUEN - HWRESERVADO) AS DISPONIBLE
				,ROW_NUMBER() over (order by HWARTCOD) R
			FROM TIGO.DETINGHW Where 1=1
			AND (HWRECBUEN - HWDESPBUEN - HWRESERVADO) >= 1  AND HWARTCOD = 'ACC0005516' )
		where R between 0 and 5
